uav.DoReduction

Source: R/uav.dimkaAlgorithm.r
uav.DoReduction.Rd

Do the reduction of targets.

uav.DoReduction(intargets, insize = 15)

Arguments

intargets

SpatialPointsDataFrame with the location of targets to reduce

insize

not used so far.

Value

A list with polygons, points and sminos with the reduced target locations.

Examples

library(goal)
data(goaldata.data2)
one = goal::uav.GenerateTargets(goaldata.data2)
#>
